10 (b) The legislature finds a central bank digital
11 currency would not provide any unique benefits to Wyoming
12 citizens or businesses compared to existing technologies
13 and poses serious risks including:
14
15 (i) Establishing a direct line between a
16 person's financial activity and government;
17
18 (ii) Easily prohibiting the purchase of certain
19 goods or limiting purchases by a person;
20
21 (iii) Reducing credit availability;
22
